in Html file, need a line for displaying the calculation and a line for displaying the number pressed. 
display "0" as default.
add all the buttons with their relevant id.
add onclick to all the buttons.
when a number or "." is pressed, display it on number pressed line. 
the number is kept adding next to the previous number until an operator is pressed.
when an operator is pressed, transfer the numbers and the operator to the calculation display line.
when pressing "=" calculate the result and display the result.
when press "AC" clear all the calculation and display.